item.title: Guitar Update 2
item.author: Author
item.description: Any anime guitar repo would be incomplete without K-On, literally the greatest guitar anime there ever was. Therefore, the Drive folder now includes K-On. Also, my guitar repos are all tabs available online, and they are made available by very good and generous people (who are much more talented than me) that made these tabs and distribute it for free (some example: vvxo, Aethersan , Tam Lu, okayan_zeak21, and Very Nize).
